data.description: This 4BR, 2 bath home has so much to offer.  Dream kitchen with center island that has bar eating, and a separate walk in pantry with barn door.  Kitchen opens up to the spacious family room that includes a corner wood-burning fireplace.  The living room is so spacious you could set-up 2 different areas.  Formal dining is just off of the kitchen and is also open to the living room.  Great home for entertaining or for family to all be together.  Split bedroom floor plan with the master BR having plenty of room to even have a sitting area, walk-in closet, and a great master bathroom complete with soaking tub and separate shower.  Guest bedrooms are all nicely sized with a jack and jill bathroom in between two of the bedrooms.  Large metal fenced backyard, separate side yard on the west, and a storage room.  Seller is offering $10,000 to a buyer for help with their lending fees or to do upgrades of your choice with an acceptable offer.  Call a realtor today to set up to see.
